OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has led his first
OL,8,FCabinet meeting since resigning as
OL,9,Fleader of the Labour Party on Monday.
OL,11,FMinisters made their way along Downing
OL,12,FStreet on Tuesday morning to shouts
OL,13,Ffrom journalists about who they might
OL,14,Fsupport as leader and whether they
OL,15,Fwould run themselves.
OL,17,FAt least one member of the Cabinet is
OL,18,Fconsidering challenging Andy Burnham
OL,19,Ffor the leadership of the Labour Party
OL,20,Fand the role of prime minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
