CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782211684
OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FChief Secretary to the Prime Minister
OL,8,FDarren Jones, a staunch Starmer
OL,9,Floyalist, is said to be weighing up a
OL,10,Fleadership bid and said he "was
OL,11,Fgetting on with the job" when asked
OL,12,Fabout this morning.
OL,14,FSources close to Jones said he would
OL,15,Fwant assurances on Burnham's approach
OL,16,Fto economic policy, as there are
OL,17,Fconcerns over potential unease in the
OL,18,Fmarkets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
