OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782211684
OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FA second potential rival to Burnham is
OL,8,Fformer Royal Marines officer Al Carns,
OL,9,Fwho is making up his mind whether to
OL,10,Flaunch a leadership campaign.
OL,12,FThe former armed forces minister said
OL,13,Fhe had not ruled out standing, telling
OL,14,FITV's Peston programme on Monday
OL,15,Fnight: "I'm not ready to make a
OL,16,Fdecision on this."
OL,18,FHe suggested he was considering what
OL,19,Fto do before nominations for the
OL,20,FLabour leadership open on July 9.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
