OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782211684
OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FThe Cabinet meeting is likely to be an
OL,8,Fawkward one, after many of Starmer's
OL,9,Ftop team turned against him and backed
OL,10,FBurnham, either publicly or behind
OL,11,Fclosed doors.
OL,13,FIt also comes after Burnham was
OL,14,Fwelcomed by around 200 MPs in
OL,15,Fparliament on Monday, including the
OL,16,FChancellor Rachel Reeves, Energy
OL,17,FSecretary Ed Miliband, Chief Whip
OL,18,FJonathan Reynolds, and Housing
OL,19,FSecretary Steve Reed, none of whom
OL,20,Fwere at Downing Street as Starmer
OL,21,Fresigned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
