CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782211684
OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FThe new Makerfield MP could be in
OL,8,FDowning Street within weeks if a
OL,9,Fchallenger does not emerge.
OL,11,FTalks are also said to be taking place
OL,12,Fabout who will sit in Burnham's
OL,13,FCabinet, with Miliband and Home
OL,14,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood both tipped
OL,15,Fas potential candidates to replace
OL,16,FRachel Reeves as chancellor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
