OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FFormer Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,8,Fannounced he was not going to run
OL,9,Fagainst Burnham on Monday. It has been
OL,10,Fwidely suggested that he has been
OL,11,Foffered a top job in return for this
OL,12,Fbacking.
OL,14,FBurnham's allies have said no jobs had
OL,15,Fbeen given and no deals had been made
OL,16,Fas of Monday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
