OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FReeves' successor would be bound by
OL,8,Fthe rules she set, which aim to
OL,9,Frestrict borrowing and pay for day-to-
OL,10,Fday spending out of tax revenues by
OL,11,Fthe end of the decade.
OL,13,FBurnham is set to give a speech on
OL,14,Ffiscal policy next week after
OL,15,Freturning as an MP following his
OL,16,FMakerfield by-election victory last
OL,17,Fweek.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
