OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FContest follows Starmer's resignation
OL,14,FStarmer announced he would be standing
OL,15,Fdown in an emotional statement outside
OL,16,FNo 10 on Monday, promising an "orderly
OL,17,Fhandover of power" to his successor.
OL,26,@xD@_OUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
