OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782211684
OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FDefending his record, he pledged to
OL,8,Fgive the next leader his "full and
OL,9,Funequivocal support, knowing that they
OL,10,Fwill inherit a Britain that is far
OL,11,Fstronger and fairer than the one I
OL,12,Finherited two years ago".
OL,14,FStarmer said he would ask Labour's
OL,15,Fruling National Executive Committee
OL,16,F(NEC) to set out a timetable that
OL,17,Fwould see a new leader in place by the
OL,18,Ftime Parliament returns from its
OL,19,Fsummer recess on September 1 if there
OL,20,Fis a contest.
OL,26,@tD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
