OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,FBut Burnham could be the only
OL,8,Fcandidate when nominations close on
OL,9,FJuly 16 and therefore he could become
OL,10,Fprime minister as early as July 17.
OL,12,FOn Monday evening, the prime minister
OL,13,Fand his wife, Lady Victoria Starmer,
OL,14,Fhosted No 10 staff, some Labour MPs
OL,15,Fand loyal cabinet members for drinks
OL,16,Fin the No 10 garden, where they
OL,17,Fthanked those present for the support
OL,18,Fthey had given.
OL,20,FLady Starmer told them: "I just wanted
OL,21,Fto say thank you from me.
OL,26,@|D@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
