OL,3,CMPs weigh up leadership as Cabinet
OL,4,Cmeets for first time since PM
OL,5,Cresignation
OL,7,F"I obviously love Keir and support him
OL,8,Fas much as I can, but there's only so
OL,9,Fmuch I could do, and it's you guys who
OL,10,Fgave that support day in, day out, and
OL,11,FI am personally really grateful for
OL,12,Fthat. So, thank you all."
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
